请为小说《{{ NovelTitle }}》中的角色「{{ CharacterName }}」生成完整角色档案。

# 角色基本信息
- 姓名：{{ CharacterName }}
- 定位：{{ CharacterRole }}
- 简介：{{ CharacterBrief }}

# 相关小说内容
{{ Summaries }}

# 要求
1. gender：性别，只能是 male / female / neutral 之一
2. age：年龄或年龄感，简短字符串，如 "16" / "约25岁" / "少年" / "中年"
3. appearance：外貌概述，一段话，100字以内（与 visual_prompt 互补，此处侧重叙事印象）
4. personality：深度性格，包含核心特质、行为模式、内在矛盾与核心恐惧
5. personality_tags：3-5个短标签，每个不超过4字，如["孤傲冷峻","腹黑算计"]
6. background：详细背景，包含出身、成长经历、重要转折
7. character_arc：角色成长轨迹，描述起点、关键转变、最终归宿
8. abilities：核心能力，每项包含 name 和 description
9. dialogue_style：说话风格（vocabulary_level / patterns 2-4条 / speech_habits 一句话总结）
10. archetype：角色原型，如英雄、智者、导师、反派、守护者、叛逆者等
{% if PromptLanguage == "en" %}9. visual_prompt (English): image generation prompt, ~150 words, covering 12 dimensions in order. No art style, quality, or rendering tags:

   [1] GENDER & BUILD: gender, age range, ethnicity, height, body type, shoulder-to-hip ratio
   [2] FACE: face shape, three-zone proportion, cheekbones, jawline, chin, eye spacing
   [3] EYES: eye shape, size, iris color (precise hue), default gaze quality
   [4] BROWS (natural): shape, density, color; natural lash length — no cosmetics
   [5] NOSE & LIPS: bridge height, tip shape, nostril width; lip fullness, cupid's bow, bare lip color and texture
   [6] SKIN: precise tone, surface finish, notable marks
   [7] HAIR: color and treatment, texture, density, length, styling, bangs
   [8] OUTFIT (layer by layer): each garment — type, cut, neckline, sleeves, hem, fabric, colors, decorative details
   [9] FOOTWEAR: type, heel, material, color
   [10] ACCESSORIES: each item — name, material, style, placement, identity significance; weapons in full detail
   [11] POSTURE: default stance, hand position, characteristic tilt
   [12] SIGNATURE ELEMENT: the single most recognizable visual detail, described with specific material/condition/placement{% else %}9. visual_prompt（中文）：图像生成提示词，约150字，按序覆盖12个维度，禁止添加画风/质量/渲染标签：

   [1] 性别体型：性别、年龄感、种族、身高、体型、肩宽、腰臀比
   [2] 面部结构：脸型、三庭比例、颧骨、下颌线、下巴形态、眼距
   [3] 眼睛：眼型、大小、精确瞳色、默认目光质感
   [4] 眉毛（自然）：眉形、密度、眉色；自然睫毛形态——禁止任何妆容描述
   [5] 鼻唇：鼻梁高度、鼻头形态、鼻翼；唇厚、唇峰、裸唇色与质感
   [6] 肤色：精确肤色描述词、肤感、特殊标记
   [7] 发型：发色与处理方式、发质、发量、发长、造型方式、刘海
   [8] 服装（逐层）：每件——品类、廓形、领口、袖型、下摆、面料、颜色、装饰细节
   [9] 鞋履：鞋型、跟高、材质、颜色
   [10] 配饰：逐件——名称、材质、风格、佩戴位置、身份关联；武器完整描述
   [11] 体态：默认站姿、手部位置、特征性倾斜
   [12] 标志性元素：最具辨识度的单一视觉细节，具体描述材质/状态/位置{% endif %}
10. 严格输出单个 JSON 对象，不含任何说明文字

# 输出格式（单个 JSON 对象）
{
  "name": "{{ CharacterName }}",
  "role": "{{ CharacterRole }}",
  "gender": "male/female/neutral",
  "age": "如 16 / 约25岁 / 少年 / 中年",
  "archetype": "角色原型",
  "appearance": "叙事性外貌概述，100字以内",
  "personality": "...",
  "personality_tags": ["...", "..."],
  "background": "...",
  "character_arc": "...",
  "abilities": [{"name": "...", "description": "..."}],
  "dialogue_style": {
    "vocabulary_level": "武侠",
    "patterns": ["...", "..."],
    "speech_habits": "..."
  },
  "visual_prompt": "按12个维度撰写的图像生成提示词，约150字"
}
